            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Address within 2-4 weeks to improve overall security posture.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100" style="background-color: var(--light-color); border-left: 6px solid #ffc107; padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <h3 style="color: #ffc107; font-family: var(--header-font);">1. Missing Security Headers</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>CVSS:</strong> 6.2 | <strong>Timeline:</strong> 2-4 weeks</p>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Missing:</strong> Content-Security-Policy, X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options, Strict-Transport-Security</p>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Action:</strong> Add security headers to Root controller finalize_headers method</p>
        </div>
    </div>

